# 🍒 Cherry Studio Cherry Studio 是一款支持多種 LLM 供應商的桌面客戶端，適用於 Windows、Mac 和 Linux。 👏 歡迎加入 [Telegram 群組](https://t.me/CherryStudioAI)｜[Discord](https://discord.gg/wez8HtpxqQ) | [QQ 群(575014769)](https://qm.qq.com/q/lo0D4qVZKi) ❤️ 喜歡 Cherry Studio 嗎？請給我們一顆星星 🌟 或 [贊助](https://raw.githubusercontent.com/CherryHQ/cherry-studio/main/docs/sponsor.md) 支持開發！ # 🌠 截圖預覽 ![](https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/36dddb2c-e0fb-4a5f-9411-91447bab6e18) ![](https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/f549e8a0-2385-40b4-b52b-2039e39f2930) ![](https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/58e0237c-4d36-40de-b428-53051d982026) # 🌟 核心特色 1. **多樣化 LLM 供應商支持**： - ☁️ 主流 LLM 雲端服務：OpenAI、Gemini、Anthropic 等 - 🔗 AI 網頁服務整合：Claude、Peplexity、Poe 及其他 - 💻 本地模型支持：Ollama、LM Studio 2. **AI 助手與對話功能**： - 📚 300+ 預設 AI 助手 - 🤖 自訂助手創建 - 💬 多模型同時對話 3. **文件與數據處理**： - 📄 支援文字、圖片、Office、PDF 等格式 - ☁️ WebDAV 檔案管理與備份 - 📊 Mermaid 圖表視覺化 - 💻 程式碼語法高亮

# 📝 Roadmap

We're actively working on the following features and improvements:

1. 🎯 **Core Features**

- Selection Assistant - Smart content selection enhancement
- Deep Research - Advanced research capabilities
- Memory System - Global context awareness
- Document Preprocessing - Improved document handling
- MCP Marketplace - Model Context Protocol ecosystem

2. 🗂 **Knowledge Management**

- Notes and Collections
- Dynamic Canvas visualization
- OCR capabilities
- TTS (Text-to-Speech) support

3. 📱 **Platform Support**

- HarmonyOS Edition (PC)
- Android App (Phase 1)
- iOS App (Phase 1)
- Multi-Window support
- Window Pinning functionality

4. 🔌 **Advanced Features**

- Plugin System
- ASR (Automatic Speech Recognition)
- Assistant and Topic Interaction Refactoring

Track our progress and contribute on our [project board](https://github.com/orgs/CherryHQ/projects/7).

Want to influence our roadmap? Join our [GitHub Discussions](https://github.com/CherryHQ/cherry-studio/discussions) to share your ideas and feedback!

# 🤝 Contributing

We welcome contributions to Cherry Studio! Here are some ways you can contribute:

1. **Contribute Code**: Develop new features or optimize existing code.
2. **Fix Bugs**: Submit fixes for any bugs you find.
3. **Maintain Issues**: Help manage GitHub issues.
4. **Product Design**: Participate in design discussions.
5. **Write Documentation**: Improve user manuals and guides.
6. **Community Engagement**: Join discussions and help users.
7. **Promote Usage**: Spread the word about Cherry Studio.

Refer to the [Branching Strategy](https://raw.githubusercontent.com/CherryHQ/cherry-studio/main/docs/branching-strategy-en.md) for contribution guidelines

## Getting Started

1. **Fork the Repository**: Fork and clone it to your local machine.
2. **Create a Branch**: For your changes.
3. **Submit Changes**: Commit and push your changes.
4. **Open a Pull Request**: Describe your changes and reasons.

For more detailed guidelines, please refer to our [Contributing Guide](https://raw.githubusercontent.com/CherryHQ/cherry-studio/main/CONTRIBUTING.md).

Thank you for your support and contributions!

# 🔧 Developer Co-creation Program

We are launching the Cherry Studio Developer Co-creation Program to foster a healthy and positive-feedback loop within the open-source ecosystem. We believe that great software is built collaboratively, and every merged pull request breathes new life into the project.

We sincerely invite you to join our ranks of contributors and shape the future of Cherry Studio with us.

## Contributor Rewards Program

To give back to our core contributors and create a virtuous cycle, we have established the following long-term incentive plan.

**The inaugural tracking period for this program will be Q3 2025 (July, August, September). Rewards for this cycle will be distributed on October 1st.**

# 🤝 貢獻指南

我們歡迎你為 Cherry Studio 貢獻！你可以這樣參與：

1. **貢獻程式碼**：開發新功能或優化現有程式。
2. **修復錯誤**：提交你發現的問題修正。
3. **維護議題**：協助管理 GitHub 問題。
4. **產品設計**：參與設計討論。
5. **撰寫文件**：改進使用手冊和指南。
6. **社群參與**：加入討論並協助使用者。
7. **推廣應用**：宣傳 Cherry Studio。

貢獻請參考 [分支策略](https://raw.githubusercontent.com/CherryHQ/cherry-studio/main/docs/branching-strategy-en.md)

## 快速開始

1. **分叉倉庫**：Fork 並複製到本地端。
2. **創建分支**：用於你的修改。
3. **提交變更**：Commit 並 Push 你的變更。
4. **發送 PR**：描述你的變更和原因。

詳細規範請參考 [貢獻指南](https://raw.githubusercontent.com/CherryHQ/cherry-studio/main/CONTRIBUTING.md)。

感謝你的支持與貢獻！

# 🔧 開發者共創計畫

我們即將啟動 Cherry Studio 開發者共創計畫，促進開源生態的健康正向循環。我們相信優秀的軟體來自協作，每個被合併的 PR 都為專案注入新生命。

誠摯邀請你加入貢獻者行列，與我們一同塑造 Cherry Studio 的未來。

## 貢獻者獎勵計畫

為回饋核心貢獻者並建立良性循環，我們制定了以下長期激勵方案。

**本計畫的首個追蹤週期為 2025 年第三季（7 月、8 月、9 月）。本周期獎勵將於 10 月 1 日發放。**

Within any tracking period (e.g., July 1st to September 30th for the first cycle), any developer who contributes more than **30 meaningful commits** to any of Cherry Studio's open-source projects on GitHub is eligible for the following benefits: - **Cursor Subscription Sponsorship**: Receive a **$70 USD** credit or reimbursement for your [Cursor](https://cursor.sh/) subscription, making AI your most efficient coding partner. - **Unlimited Model Access**: Get **unlimited** API calls for the **DeepSeek** and **Qwen** models. - **Cutting-Edge Tech Access**: Enjoy occasional perks, including API access to models like **Claude**, **Gemini**, and **OpenAI**, keeping you at the forefront of technology. ## Growing Together & Future Plans A vibrant community is the driving force behind any sustainable open-source project. As Cherry Studio grows, so will our rewards program. We are committed to continuously aligning our benefits with the best-in-class tools and resources in the industry. This ensures our core contributors receive meaningful support, creating a positive cycle where developers, the community, and the project grow together. **Moving forward, the project will also embrace an increasingly open stance to give back to the entire open-source community.** ## How to Get Started? We look forward to your first Pull Request! You can start by exploring our repositories, picking up a `good first issue`, or proposing your own enhancements. Every commit is a testament to the spirit of open source. Thank you for your interest and contributions. Let's build together. # 🏢 Enterprise Edition Building on the Community Edition, we are proud to introduce **Cherry Studio Enterprise Edition**—a privately deployable AI productivity and management platform designed for modern teams and enterprises. The Enterprise Edition addresses core challenges in team collaboration by centralizing the management of AI resources, knowledge, and data. It empowers organizations to enhance efficiency, foster innovation, and ensure compliance, all while maintaining 100% control over their data in a secure environment. ## Core Advantages - **Unified Model Management**: Centrally integrate and manage various cloud-based LLMs (e.g., OpenAI, Anthropic, Google Gemini) and locally deployed private models. Employees can use them out-of-the-box without individual configuration. - **Enterprise-Grade Knowledge Base**: Build, manage, and share team-wide knowledge bases. Ensure knowledge is retained and consistent, enabling team members to interact with AI based on unified and accurate information. - **Fine-Grained Access Control**: Easily manage employee accounts and assign role-based permissions for different models, knowledge bases, and features through a unified admin backend. - **Fully Private Deployment**: Deploy the entire backend service on your on-premises servers or private cloud, ensuring your data remains 100% private and under your control to meet the strictest security and compliance standards. - **Reliable Backend Services**: Provides stable API services, enterprise-grade data backup and recovery mechanisms to ensure business continuity. ## ✨ Online Demo > 🚧 **Public Beta Notice** > > The Enterprise Edition is currently in its early public beta stage, and we are actively iterating and optimizing its features. We are aware that it may not be perfectly stable yet. If you encounter any issues or have valuable suggestions during your trial, we would be very grateful if you could contact us via email to provide feedback. **🔗 [Cherry Studio Enterprise](https://www.cherry-ai.com/enterprise)** ## Version Comparison | Feature | Community Edition | Enterprise Edition | | :---------------- | :----------------------------------------- | :-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- | | **Open Source** | ✅ Yes | ⭕️ part. released to cust. | | **Cost** | Free for Personal Use / Commercial License | Buyout / Subscription Fee | | **Admin Backend** | — | ● Centralized **Model** Access
● **Employee** Management
● Shared **Knowledge Base**
● **Access** Control
● **Data** Backup | | **Server** | — | ✅ Dedicated Private Deployment | ## Get the Enterprise Edition We believe the Enterprise Edition will become your team's AI productivity engine. If you are interested in Cherry Studio Enterprise Edition and would like to learn more, request a quote, or schedule a demo, please contact us. - **For Business Inquiries & Purchasing**: **📧 [bd@cherry-ai.com](https://raw.githubusercontent.com/CherryHQ/cherry-studio/main/mailto:bd@cherry-ai.com)** # 🔗 Related Projects - [one-api](https://github.com/songquanpeng/one-api):LLM API management and distribution system, supporting mainstream models like OpenAI, Azure, and Anthropic. 在任何追蹤週期內（例如第一輪為 7 月 1 日至 9 月 30 日），任何對 Cherry Studio 在 GitHub 上的開源專案貢獻超過 **30 次有意義提交** 的開發者，皆有資格獲得以下福利： - **Cursor 訂閱贊助**：獲得 **$70 美元** 的 [Cursor](https://cursor.sh/) 訂閱抵用金或報銷，讓 AI 成為你最高效的編碼夥伴。 - **模型無限存取**：獲得 **DeepSeek** 和 **Qwen** 模型的 **API 無限調用**權限。 - **前沿技術特權**：享有如 **Claude**、**Gemini**、**OpenAI** 等模型的 API 使用權等不定期福利，讓你始終站在技術前沿。 ## 共同成長與未來規劃 一個充滿活力的社群，是任何可持續發展開源專案的核心驅動力。隨著 Cherry Studio 的成長，我們的獎勵計畫也會持續進化。我們承諾將福利與業界最優秀的工具和資源保持同步，確保核心貢獻者獲得實質支持，建立正向循環，讓開發者、社群與專案共同成長。 **未來，專案也將持續擁抱更開放的姿態，回饋整個開源社群。** ## 如何開始？ 我們期待你的第一個 Pull Request！ 你可以從瀏覽我們的倉庫、挑選 `good first issue` 或提出自己的優化建議開始。每一筆提交都是對開源精神的見證。 感謝你的關注與貢獻。 讓我們一起共創未來。 # 🏢 企業版 在社群版的基礎上，我們自豪地推出 **Cherry Studio 企業版**——一個可私有部署的 AI 生產力與管理平台，專為現代團隊及企業設計。 企業版針對團隊協作中的核心挑戰，集中管理 AI 資源、知識與數據。讓企業提升效率、促進創新並確保合規，同時在安全環境下 100% 掌控自有數據。 ## 核心優勢 - **統一模型管理**：集中整合與管理雲端 LLM（如 OpenAI、Anthropic、Google Gemini）及本地私有模型。員工開箱即用，無需個別配置。 - **企業級知識庫**：構建、管理並分享團隊級知識庫。確保知識傳承一致，團隊成員基於統一且正確資訊與 AI 互動。 - **細緻權限管控**：輕鬆管理員工帳號，透過統一後台為不同模型、知識庫和功能分配基於角色的權限。 - **全私有部署**：將整套後端服務部署於本地伺服器或私有雲，數據 100% 私有且可控，符合最嚴格安全與合規標準。 - **高可用後端服務**：提供穩定 API 服務、企業級數據備份與恢復機制，保障業務持續運行。 ## ✨ 線上演示 > 🚧 **公測版公告** > > 企業版目前處於早期公開測試階段，功能正在積極迭代與優化。我們意識到尚未完全穩定。若您在體驗期間遇到問題或有寶貴建議，非常歡迎您來信反饋，我們將不勝感激。 **🔗 [Cherry Studio 企業版](https://www.cherry-ai.com/enterprise)** ## 版本比較 | 功能 | 社群版 | 企業版 | | :---------------- | :-------------------------------------------- | :----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- | | **開源** | ✅ 是 | ⭕️ 部分釋出給客戶 | | **收費** | 個人免費 / 商業授權 | 買斷 / 訂閱收費 | | **管理後台** | — | ● 統一**模型**存取

● **數據**備份 | | **伺服器** | — | ✅ 專屬私有部署 | ## 取得企業版 我們相信企業版將成為您團隊的 AI 生產力引擎。如您有意了解 Cherry Studio 企業版、申請報價或預約演示，歡迎聯絡我們。 - **商務諮詢與購買**： **📧 [bd@cherry-ai.com](https://raw.githubusercontent.com/CherryHQ/cherry-studio/main/mailto:bd@cherry-ai.com)** # 🔗 相關專案 - [one-api](https://github.com/songquanpeng/one-api)：LLM API 管理與分發系統，支持主流模型如 OpenAI、Azure、Anthropic。特點為統一 API 介面，適合金鑰管理與二次分發。 - [ublacklist](https://github.com/iorate/ublacklist)：阻擋指定網站在 Google 搜尋結果中出現 # 🚀 貢獻者

RowTranslations.translatedContent: 在任何追蹤週期內（例如第一輪為 7 月 1 日至 9 月 30 日），任何對 Cherry Studio 在 GitHub 上的開源專案貢獻超過 **30 次有意義提交** 的開發者，皆有資格獲得以下福利：

RowTranslations.originContent: Within any tracking period (e.g., July 1st to September 30th for the first cycle), any developer who contributes more than **30 meaningful commits** to any of Cherry Studio's open-source projects on GitHub is eligible for the following benefits:

RowTranslations.translatedContent: - **Cursor 訂閱贊助**：獲得 **$70 美元** 的 [Cursor](https://cursor.sh/) 訂閱抵用金或報銷，讓 AI 成為你最高效的編碼夥伴。

RowTranslations.originContent: - **Cursor Subscription Sponsorship**: Receive a **$70 USD** credit or reimbursement for your [Cursor](https://cursor.sh/) subscription, making AI your most efficient coding partner.
RowTranslations.translatedContent: - **模型無限存取**：獲得 **DeepSeek** 和 **Qwen** 模型的 **API 無限調用**權限。

RowTranslations.originContent: - **Unlimited Model Access**: Get **unlimited** API calls for the **DeepSeek** and **Qwen** models.
RowTranslations.translatedContent: - **前沿技術特權**：享有如 **Claude**、**Gemini**、**OpenAI** 等模型的 API 使用權等不定期福利，讓你始終站在技術前沿。

RowTranslations.originContent: - **Cutting-Edge Tech Access**: Enjoy occasional perks, including API access to models like **Claude**, **Gemini**, and **OpenAI**, keeping you at the forefront of technology.

RowTranslations.translatedContent: 一個充滿活力的社群，是任何可持續發展開源專案的核心驅動力。隨著 Cherry Studio 的成長，我們的獎勵計畫也會持續進化。我們承諾將福利與業界最優秀的工具和資源保持同步，確保核心貢獻者獲得實質支持，建立正向循環，讓開發者、社群與專案共同成長。

RowTranslations.originContent: A vibrant community is the driving force behind any sustainable open-source project. As Cherry Studio grows, so will our rewards program. We are committed to continuously aligning our benefits with the best-in-class tools and resources in the industry. This ensures our core contributors receive meaningful support, creating a positive cycle where developers, the community, and the project grow together.

RowTranslations.translatedContent: **未來，專案也將持續擁抱更開放的姿態，回饋整個開源社群。**

RowTranslations.originContent: **Moving forward, the project will also embrace an increasingly open stance to give back to the entire open-source community.**

RowTranslations.translatedContent: 我們期待你的第一個 Pull Request！

RowTranslations.originContent: We look forward to your first Pull Request!

RowTranslations.translatedContent: 你可以從瀏覽我們的倉庫、挑選 `good first issue` 或提出自己的優化建議開始。每一筆提交都是對開源精神的見證。

RowTranslations.originContent: You can start by exploring our repositories, picking up a `good first issue`, or proposing your own enhancements. Every commit is a testament to the spirit of open source.
Thank you for your interest and contributions.

RowTranslations.translatedContent: 在社群版的基礎上，我們自豪地推出 **Cherry Studio 企業版**——一個可私有部署的 AI 生產力與管理平台，專為現代團隊及企業設計。

RowTranslations.originContent: Building on the Community Edition, we are proud to introduce **Cherry Studio Enterprise Edition**—a privately deployable AI productivity and management platform designed for modern teams and enterprises.

RowTranslations.translatedContent: 企業版針對團隊協作中的核心挑戰，集中管理 AI 資源、知識與數據。讓企業提升效率、促進創新並確保合規，同時在安全環境下 100% 掌控自有數據。

RowTranslations.originContent: The Enterprise Edition addresses core challenges in team collaboration by centralizing the management of AI resources, knowledge, and data. It empowers organizations to enhance efficiency, foster innovation, and ensure compliance, all while maintaining 100% control over their data in a secure environment.

RowTranslations.translatedContent: - **統一模型管理**：集中整合與管理雲端 LLM（如 OpenAI、Anthropic、Google Gemini）及本地私有模型。員工開箱即用，無需個別配置。

RowTranslations.originContent: - **Unified Model Management**: Centrally integrate and manage various cloud-based LLMs (e.g., OpenAI, Anthropic, Google Gemini) and locally deployed private models. Employees can use them out-of-the-box without individual configuration.
RowTranslations.translatedContent: - **企業級知識庫**：構建、管理並分享團隊級知識庫。確保知識傳承一致，團隊成員基於統一且正確資訊與 AI 互動。

RowTranslations.originContent: - **Enterprise-Grade Knowledge Base**: Build, manage, and share team-wide knowledge bases. Ensure knowledge is retained and consistent, enabling team members to interact with AI based on unified and accurate information.
RowTranslations.translatedContent: - **細緻權限管控**：輕鬆管理員工帳號，透過統一後台為不同模型、知識庫和功能分配基於角色的權限。

RowTranslations.originContent: - **Fine-Grained Access Control**: Easily manage employee accounts and assign role-based permissions for different models, knowledge bases, and features through a unified admin backend.
RowTranslations.translatedContent: - **全私有部署**：將整套後端服務部署於本地伺服器或私有雲，數據 100% 私有且可控，符合最嚴格安全與合規標準。

RowTranslations.originContent: - **Fully Private Deployment**: Deploy the entire backend service on your on-premises servers or private cloud, ensuring your data remains 100% private and under your control to meet the strictest security and compliance standards.
RowTranslations.translatedContent: - **高可用後端服務**：提供穩定 API 服務、企業級數據備份與恢復機制，保障業務持續運行。

RowTranslations.originContent: - **Reliable Backend Services**: Provides stable API services, enterprise-grade data backup and recovery mechanisms to ensure business continuity.

RowTranslations.translatedContent: > 企業版目前處於早期公開測試階段，功能正在積極迭代與優化。我們意識到尚未完全穩定。若您在體驗期間遇到問題或有寶貴建議，非常歡迎您來信反饋，我們將不勝感激。

RowTranslations.originContent: > The Enterprise Edition is currently in its early public beta stage, and we are actively iterating and optimizing its features. We are aware that it may not be perfectly stable yet. If you encounter any issues or have valuable suggestions during your trial, we would be very grateful if you could contact us via email to provide feedback.
